  "3139620": {
    "name": "战线危机",
    "steam_appid": 3139620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色汇总：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·   简化的RTS+致敬经典</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·   策略与操作独立存在，颇具深度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·   我不喜欢肉鸽、词条，我喜欢独特的BOSS战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️支持本地双人-绝无分手元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/ddc6018872015725fc8084e87dd20c68.poster.avif?t=1772021743\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/ddc6018872015725fc8084e87dd20c68.webm?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/ddc6018872015725fc8084e87dd20c68.mp4?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是一个忠实的RTS游戏玩家。但它在操作上的苛刻要求可能会让人望而却步。所以我希望打造一款操作简单+策略深度+有操作感的RTS游戏。在这里我们只控制一台机甲，它不仅能行走、射击、消灭虫子；甚至还可以采集、建造和召唤。这款游戏承载了我的情怀，我希望通过它，将这份热情传递给更多的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/99574b9ee71bfb1062cf76a12846a0e7.poster.avif?t=1772021743\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/99574b9ee71bfb1062cf76a12846a0e7.webm?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/99574b9ee71bfb1062cf76a12846a0e7.mp4?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战前阶段：</strong>你可以从容地进行策略布防，思考和构建各种不同的防御模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>作战阶段：</strong>你只需要实现自己的布防，并全力输出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是资源收集、基地建设还是进攻手段，这个游戏都不能一劳永逸，它需要你保持思考和操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/8fb5e432b56a3c5ddb077def6912f061.poster.avif?t=1772021743\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/8fb5e432b56a3c5ddb077def6912f061.webm?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/8fb5e432b56a3c5ddb077def6912f061.mp4?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这并不是一个Roguelike游戏。游戏采用逐一关卡推进展开，每关结尾都有独具特色的boss战，击败它就会解锁新的道具，进而丰富我们的构筑体系。我不是一个喜欢读词条的人，因此我尽量简化了每个模块的理解成本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且在游戏中，你还可以与伙伴携手战斗，共同抵御无情的虫群！两个人分属陆军和空军，互相协助互相补充。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/2ff2bbf29c4ead2ccb3e5a5d15c954c7.poster.avif?t=1772021743\" width=614 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/2ff2bbf29c4ead2ccb3e5a5d15c954c7.webm?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139620/extras/2ff2bbf29c4ead2ccb3e5a5d15c954c7.mp4?t=1772021743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中讲诉了在遥远的未来，人类文明面临着前所未有的能源危机。而在外太空发现的新型能源【原力】成为炙手可热的财富，围绕【原力】的争夺，人类和凶残的外星虫群展开了旷日持久的战争。在战争末期人类和虫族都掌握了对方的基因序列，并以此创建了许多半人半虫战士，我们似乎能在战场上见到自己被异化的曾经的战友。战争吞噬着无数的生命。并且我们似乎忘记了自己真正的敌人是谁。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 俄语, 日语, 波兰语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 韩语, 土耳其语",
